Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:10.78,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Okazaki, it's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:17.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:19.85,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I'm here to wake you up, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:53.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Where's Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:56.14,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Oh, by the time I got here, he wasn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:00.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry for you having to make breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:03.16,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I'm the one who needs to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:06.29,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I should have been more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:11.45,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,But you got suspended in place of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:13.72,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm still thinking…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:18.97,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,…that maybe I should run to\Nthe faculty office and tell them the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's the one thing I don't want you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:25.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I told you; I need you to become\Nthe student council president no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.99,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,For the sake of the drama club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:28.80,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:31.61,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.34,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.85,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Please join us if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:40.29,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Well, well. I haven't had a breakfast like this in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.53,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'll accept the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:44.42,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Let me sit next to you, Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:48.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.05,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Okazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:57.09,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,411.75)}Episode 18
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:57.09,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}Strategy for a Comeback
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:03.41,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Bomb-a-head…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:11.95,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,God… What's this so early in the…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A girl's here to confess her love to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:15.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Seriously, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.97,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Wow, what the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.38,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The rugby club?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.01,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Are you a lingerie burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.34,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Forget that, that's men's underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:29.07,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:30.70,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Coincidences are scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.19,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Is it fun for you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Think of it as an alarm clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:43.20,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I've actually lost my mind several times because of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:48.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm going to head out to school soon. Are you planning to stay here all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:51.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. Give my regards to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:56.34,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,He got suspended instead of Sakagami-san… {ep 17}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.83,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Really, he doesn't know how to keep himself out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:05.16,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Will it be okay? Won't it affect his future?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.17,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm very worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:11.03,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,The President is sick, and Tomoya is suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.43,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Will we be able to take part\Nin the School Festival like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's been three days, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:28.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why do I keep thinking about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.77,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey! We're here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:37.09,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,It seems you were caught in\Na sticky situation, Okazaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:39.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.62,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What? Who did you think it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, no one in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:49.90,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Come to think of, if you're suspended, shouldn't you be at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But who's the one dragging me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:54.93,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Where are we going, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:55.99,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:00.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They've set the atmosphere in here pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:03.24,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If it's a fortune-telling game, Ryou can enjoy it, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right, put your name in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.20,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.65,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,U-Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:09.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.62,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's the symbol for a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.81,Note,,0,0,0,,Friends - Lovers - Married
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.94,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,The couple's relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.93,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Come on, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:26.41,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,O-Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:28.64,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,But it says to put each other's hands on top of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.59,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:39.96,Note,,0,0,0,,Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.03,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Wha… What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:49.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Damn you! That hurt, Kyou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:52.48,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's because you made that choice that ruins the mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:57.06,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,In a case like that, you're supposed to choose “lover” for the sake of situational entertainment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:02.12,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,A kind woman and a man with a strong sense of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.91,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You two get along very well as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:09.04,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Whether you can progress in your relationship depends on how each of you feels…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:11.80,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What a mundane answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:14.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Isn't all fortune-telling like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:18.58,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,But I'm glad to see nothing like “horrible match” came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:20.20,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.19,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I've got something to do, so I've got to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:24.23,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tomoya, make sure you walk Ryou home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:30.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You really like stuff like that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:34.65,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,All girls like fortune-telling at the genetic level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But in your case, you can't expect much accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:41.78,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,You're right. I never get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:43.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, so you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:49.55,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Of course, it's a pity I can't get it right, but I think it's better that I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:51.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:07:02.18,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,If the results come true, it's as if there's only one future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:07.03,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,But if it fails, we can think that other futures exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:12.77,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,We never know how the future shifts because of the slightest change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:19.62,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I want to believe that in our future\Nthere are many possibilities waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't have to come on Sundays, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:31.55,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Let me do as I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:33.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Where's Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.29,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,He just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.55,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Are things not going well with your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.80,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's not something I should be meddling in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How's the presidential campaign coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Isn't the vote happening soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.64,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,It's going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:55.72,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:00.54,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Good morning. A little gift for you. {ep 17}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.15,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi! Puhi! {ep 17}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.69,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Onee-chan insisted on coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, um, ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.04,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Okazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:10.38,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Do we have a guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.42,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.50,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:14.50,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Kyou-chan, Ryou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.49,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:19.67,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,What brings even Kotomi-chan here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:23.31,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I made some food for you, Tomoya-kun. {ep 17}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:26.05,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be hungry alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:36.30,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,The air in here is heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.16,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:40.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't possibly eat all of this…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:43.52,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Ryou and I made this after waking up at five.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.54,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Of course, you will eat it, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:49.23,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I am the one responsible for getting\NOkazaki suspended, thus making me involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.95,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I have an obligation to look after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.54,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What do you mean “involved”?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:54.93,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You make it sound like we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.71,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Frankly speaking, you aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:59.56,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I don't think you all are related to this matter at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:04.06,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Excuse me, we've known him since junior year and are part of the drama club, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:07.39,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Time and titles do not matter\Nwith regards to the bonds between people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:12.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, you two. Don't get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:14.27,Default,2,0,0,0,,It's because you won't make up your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even if you say that…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:19.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fujibayashi, help me out here a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.11,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I want…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:23.62,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,…you to eat my cooking, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.04,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,K-Kotomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:31.55,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:32.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:37.92,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I worked hard on these,\Nand I've been preparing them since last night, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:42.27,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.76,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:47.23,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko brought some food, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:50.03,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, please leave this to Fuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:51.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, seriously stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:54.02,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko fully understands how you all feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:58.10,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,However, Okazaki-san should choose Fuuko's cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.62,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Starfish baumkuchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.11,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Starfish cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:03.04,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Starfish cream puffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.37,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,They look gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.96,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Okazaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:09.82,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Please eat my bento.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:11.84,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My dishes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.20,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Come on, eat up. {ep 17}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.66,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You know what choice you should be making.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:16.84,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi puhi…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.40,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Pick the best choice, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:18.70,Default-alt,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:21.42,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.17,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Best…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:22.88,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Choice…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:30.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Good work out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't be so loud…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:35.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I ate too much yesterday, so I have horrible heartburn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:39.14,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Are you sure you have the time to lie around like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:41.16,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,…when Tomoyo's in big trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.19,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:45.68,Note,Girl,0,0,0,,Gang Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:49.69,Note,,0,0,0,,Violent Tramp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:45.65,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I heard she was a big shot\Ngang member before coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:49.67,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,The other day, guys from another school came to get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.02,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,But that's related to Okazaki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.03,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.05,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, he's right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:56.55,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.06,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What? A match?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:08.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. If we lose, we'll pick up balls or do whatever you want us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.79,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hold on just a moment. I'll go talk to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.85,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Will this really increase support?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's the same idea as when we played basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.36,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I've never done anything more than play catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:29.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We have\Nthe super athlete, Sunohara, with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:31.24,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,That makes me even more worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:32.22,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:34.37,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You got yourself a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.90,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,But, under one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:41.65,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,If you guys lose, we'll have Sakagami join the women's softball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:47.92,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:57.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Tomoyo! Get three outs and we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:12:00.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If anyone gets on base safely, we lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.64,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,All right, bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.07,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:13.75,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey now…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:17.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What is she doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.45,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Shut up! You're distracting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:22.97,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,If you dare end this with a walk,\NI'll forever call you Heart of a Chicken! {lit. Flea}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.19,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We want a pitcher, not a belly itcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:26.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Calm down, Tomoyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.65,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Sunohara is pissing me off, so I can't concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:32.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,In that case, aim for Sunohara's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thinking of blasting him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.36,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,His face…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:39.44,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.73,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We want a pitcher, not a belly itcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.28,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Bring it on, Chicken Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.59,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,S-Strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:54.07,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.55,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Strike, batter out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:06.82,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,This feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We won, Tomoyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:12.81,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Did you hear about the junior, Sakagami Tomoyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:15.68,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,She had a match against\Nthe baseball team and won, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:18.69,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Wow, as expected from Tomoyo-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.56,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I'll go watch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.32,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:30.59,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You made all the bad rumors vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:31.51,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:34.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's for the sake of the drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:36.03,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Even so, I'm grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:38.46,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,At this rate, I think I can achieve my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:40.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.55,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Right, I haven't told you about it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:49.30,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I want to preserve the sakura trees here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.49,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,There's a plan to cut them all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.98,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,The students that know about it don't like the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.77,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,People living around here are against it, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:03.32,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,If I become the student council president of this school,\NI can act to preserve these sakura trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:07.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You transferred here just for that? {ep 17}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:08.76,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Yeah. {ep 17}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.93,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I wanted to preserve this place no matter what. {ep 17}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.98,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,It's a very important place. {ep 17}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.53,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What were you like as a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:25.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.08,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I had gone wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.51,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What do you think people become…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:34.96,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Or rather, what do you think keeps people from going wild?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Talents, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:42.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you have a talent, you can have\Na clear image of what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:44.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You can let yourself be absorbed in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:46.10,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,That's a good answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.06,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Then, what if you can't find a talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:50.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Maybe relationships?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.54,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I see. That's a plausible answer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:58.79,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,The answer I found is “family”.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:02.26,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,When there's family, it's easier to control oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:04.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not always!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There are cases where family causes one to have a wild life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:10.11,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,The “family” I'm talking about doesn't have to be a real family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.28,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,It can even be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:15.94,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What it takes is a group that's like a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:21.85,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I don't mean to force the answer on others, but that's the answer I arrived at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.34,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,My parents didn't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.74,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Inside my house it was totally cold, and there was no communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:31.32,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Not even any arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.13,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Neither had done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:41.75,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,But I'm sure small misunderstandings and hardships accumulated, and eventually, things no longer clicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.83,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I had gone wild for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:50.00,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I forced my anger and irritation on anyone and everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:52.68,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I was a weak person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:56.98,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,The one who woke me up was…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.77,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,…my younger brother, Takafumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:04.21,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,A quiet, moderate, and kind guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.49,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,But I wasn't a good sister at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:13.28,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I'd never seen him smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:19.34,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Two years ago, my parents were going to get divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:23.96,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,They fought over who'd take the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:27.89,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I didn't care how it ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:31.43,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,But Takafumi didn't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.56,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,He didn't want to go with either one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.57,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,It was the first time he said anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:39.97,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:42.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He jumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:47.33,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Yeah. He said he'd jump\Nif they were going to get divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.06,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,And he really did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.78,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I don't understand at all why he did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.28,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,It's not as though he wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:17:00.20,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I don't think even he understood the rationale behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:07.78,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,But, with him doing that, we finally became a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:12.86,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,He was ice cold, and we thought there was nothing we could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:22.26,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,When spring came, he was finally discharged, and we walked down the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:25.06,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,He said to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:29.82,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,“I want to come and see these sakura every year with everyone, as a family.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:36.73,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I felt the same way… and so did my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.12,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,The city will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:50.08,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,But there are many people who treasure these sakura trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.41,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:55.71,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Many people who live in this city feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:18:01.19,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,No matter how depressing a place may look, the most important places don't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:06.50,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I think there's a similar aspect to family, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.50,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Nagisa! Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:16.38,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,It really has been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:18.57,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you're better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I worried all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:23.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:32.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I heard you got yourself suspended to make Sakagami-san the student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:35.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I have no clue how I should even begin to apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It wasn't solely for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:41.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I did it for the drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:45.92,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If you phrase it like that, it sounds condescending.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ah, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:49.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:53.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you want to take responsibility,\Nthen help Tomoyo with her matches after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:58.82,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,It'll be a one-set match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:01.34,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,If I win, I'll have you join the tennis team.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.59,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Agreed. Let's have a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.79,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I wish she was playing a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:09.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Will Sakagami-san be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:15.19,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,There's a huge audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.83,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Okazaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:18.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:19.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:22.99,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:27.20,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,The match's already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:35.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're keeping a good pace for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:36.39,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:39.84,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sakagami-san, would you like a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:41.99,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I don't need it now. Thank you though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:37.96,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Are they changing courts next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:38.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.46,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,We've met before, too, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:45.36,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You're…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:47.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm Furukawa Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:49.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm trying to reestablish the drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.58,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,The drama club…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:55.37,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I see, so that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:57.66,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:58.41,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I'm going out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:29.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:29.89,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:30.59,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.07,Default-alt,Guy,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.30,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:34.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:36.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:39.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That was Sakagami-san's point, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.33,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,We need to treat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:44.84,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You should go to the health center.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:55.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's go to the health center.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:57.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:01.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'll walk slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:01.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:21.89,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Well, I knew it all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:22.73,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.26,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Onee-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:28.04,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:32.05,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:37.21,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Come on, what are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:52.98,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry… I'm sorry…
