Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:43.60,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Congratulations on getting\Nthe drama club reestablished.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.60,0:23:46.86,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I made lots of food to celebrate the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:53.99,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If it hadn't been for everyone here,\NI don't think I could have done a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:59.24,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,It's just been your father around since you were little, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:02.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Despite living in the same house, we carry on with our lives separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.45,0:24:07.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Pops and I haven't been family for a long time.
